{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-css-flexbox-by-building-a-photo-gallery/step-6","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"learn-css-flexbox-by-building-a-photo-gallery","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 6","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sledeći, dodeli svakom <code>img</code> svojstvo elementa <code>src</code> prema njegovom redosledu u dokumentu. <code>img</code> prvi treba da ima <code>src</code> od <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/1.jpg</code>. Preostali neka budu isti, osim što promeniš <code>1</code> sa brojem koji <code>img</code> u dokumentu.</p>\n</section>","id":"61537d86bdc3dd343688fceb","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-css-flexbox-by-building-a-photo-gallery/step-6"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\">\r\n  <head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Photo Gallery</title>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./styles.css\">\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <header class=\"header\">\r\n      <h1>css flexbox photo gallery</h1>\r\n    </header>\r\n    <div class=\"gallery\">\r\n      <img>\r\n      <img>\r\n      <img>\r\n      <img>\r\n      <img>\r\n      <img>\r\n      <img>\r\n      <img>\r\n      <img>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[12,24],"history":["index.html"]},{"fileKey":"stylescss","ext":"css","name":"styles","contents":"","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["styles.css"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Sve devet elemenata od <code>img</code> moraju imati svojstvo elementa <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"const images = [...document.querySelectorAll('img')];\r\nassert(images.every(image => image.getAttribute('src')));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš prvi element za <code>img</code> treba da ima <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/1.jpg</code> postavljen kao vrednost atributa elementa za <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[0]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/1.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Drugi element vašeg <code>img</code> mora imati <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/2.jpg</code> postavljen kao vrednost svojstva elementa za <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[1]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/2.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj treći element od <code>img</code> treba da ima <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/3.jpg</code> postavljen kao vrednost atributa elemenata <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[2]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/3.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj četvrti element od <code>img</code> treba da ima <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/4.jpg</code> postavljeno kao vrednost svojstva polja <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[3]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/4.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj peti element <code>img</code> treba da ima <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/5.jpg</code> postavljen kao vrednost atributa elementa <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[4]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/5.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Tvoje šesto polje od <code>img</code> mora imati <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/6.jpg</code> postavljeno kao vrednost svojstva za <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[5]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/6.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Element vašeg sedmog <code>img</code> mora imati <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/7.jpg</code> postavljeno kao vrednost atributa elementa za <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[6]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/7.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj osmi element od <code>img</code> mora imati <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/8.jpg</code> postavljeno kao vrednost svojstva elemenata <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[7]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/8.jpg');"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj deveti element za <code>img</code> treba da ima <code>https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/9.jpg</code> postavljen kao vrednost atributa elemenata <code>src</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(document.querySelectorAll('img')?.[8]?.getAttribute('src') === 'https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/9.jpg');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/#learn-css-flexbox-by-building-a-photo-gallery","dashedName":"step-6","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"2022/responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-css-flexbox-by-building-a-photo-gallery","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-css-flexbox-by-building-a-photo-gallery/step-7","prevChallengePath":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-css-flexbox-by-building-a-photo-gallery/step-5","id":"61537d86bdc3dd343688fceb","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\">\r\n  <head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>Photo Gallery</title>\r\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./styles.css\">\r\n  </head>\r\n  <body>\r\n    <header class=\"header\">\r\n      <h1>css flexbox photo gallery</h1>\r\n    </header>\r\n    <div class=\"gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/1.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/2.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/3.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/4.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/5.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/6.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/7.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/8.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/css-photo-gallery/9.jpg\" alt=\"Gallery\">\r\n    </div>\r\n  </body>\r\n</html>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"},{"name":"styles","ext":"css","contents":"* {\r\n  box-sizing: border-box;\r\n}\r\n\r\nbody {\r\n  margin: 0;\r\n  font-family: sans-serif;\r\n  background: #f5f6f7;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.header {\r\n  text-align: center;\r\n  text-transform: uppercase;\r\n  padding: 32px;\r\n  background-color: #0a0a23;\r\n  color: #fff;\r\n  border-bottom: 4px solid #fdb347;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.gallery {\r\n  display: flex;\r\n  flex-direction: row;\r\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\r\n  justify-content: center;\r\n  align-items: center;\r\n  gap: 16px;\r\n  max-width: 1400px;\r\n  margin: 0 auto;\r\n  padding: 20px 10px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.gallery img {\r\n  width: 100%;\r\n  max-width: 350px;\r\n  height: 300px;\r\n  object-fit: cover;\r\n  border-radius: 10px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.gallery::after {\r\n  content: \"\";\r\n  width: 350px;\r\n}","history":["styles.css"],"fileKey":"stylescss"}]}},"id":"/learn/2022/responsive-web-design/learn-css-flexbox-by-building-a-photo-gallery/step-6"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}